  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The Risk Management Plan&amp;nbsp;describes the approach that will be used to identify, analyze, prioritize, monitor, and&#xD;
    mitigate risks. It details the risk management tasks that will be carried out, assigned responsibilities, and any&#xD;
    additional resources required for the risk management activity. On a smaller scale project, this plan may be embedded&#xD;
    within the Software Development Plan.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The Risk Management Plan should be updated when risks or mitigation strategies change.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&lt;!--EndFragment--></mainDescription>
  <purpose>&lt;a id=&quot;Top&quot; name=&quot;Top&quot;>&lt;/a>&lt;a id=&quot;XE_Risk_Management_Plan_document__as_artifact&quot;&#xD;
name=&quot;XE_Risk_Management_Plan_document__as_artifact&quot;>&lt;/a>&lt;a id=&quot;XE_Risk_Management_Plan_document__purpose_of&quot;&#xD;
name=&quot;XE_Risk_Management_Plan_document__purpose_of&quot;>&lt;/a>&lt;a id=&quot;Purpose&quot; name=&quot;Purpose&quot;>&lt;/a> &#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    To ensure that project risks are properly identified, analyzed, documented, mitigated, monitored, and controlled.&#xD;
&lt;/p></purpose>
